column5: I relate to this so much. Every random pain and my brain automatically goes to cancer. Or ALS, that’s also a fun one!

YTA. Why do you hate glass jars so much? Seems like a weird thing to get upset over. Also you did something bad so OF COURSE you should feel bad. Apologize and hope she doesn’t dump your glass-jar hating ass.
